properties.name: El Chapultepec
properties.description: Posted by Josephine1962 Market St, Denver, COEl Chapultepec has been hosting jazz and blues notables since 1951, including the likes of Frank Sinatra and Tony Bennett. The place is small and usually crowded, but it\'s known throughout Denver as the city\'s best venue for live blues and jazz. A limited menu of drinks and Mexican food is offered, and you\'ll want to try the burritos, which are almost as legendary as the performers. Live music every single night, and never a cover charge! Two drink minimum per set.
